📊 Zepto Sales Data Analysis Project

This project focuses on analyzing sales data from Zepto, a fast-growing quick commerce platform in India. 
The goal is to extract meaningful business insights using Python-based data analysis techniques.

🚀 Project Overview
Performed data cleaning and preprocessing
Conducted exploratory data analysis (EDA)
Visualized trends using Matplotlib & Seaborn
Derived insights related to:
Sales performance
City-wise distribution
Product/category trends

🛠️ Tech Stack
Python 🐍
Pandas
NumPy
Matplotlib
Seaborn
Jupyter Notebook

📈 Key Analysis Performed
Handling missing values and data formatting
Aggregation of sales by city and category
Visualization of:
Sales distribution
Top-performing locations
Product demand trends
Identification of patterns to support business decisions

📷 Sample Insights
Certain cities contribute significantly higher sales
Product categories show varying demand patterns
Visualizations help in quick decision-making

📂 Project Structure
Zepto_Project.ipynb → Main analysis notebook
Cleaned dataset and visual outputs inside notebook
